    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Privilegium de Ruberino, quod est prope Fornovum In nomine domini nostri
                        Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName ref="#people/110" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Hludovicus</persName>, gratia Dei <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperator</rs> augustus. Omnium fi|delium Sancte Dei Ęcclesie ac
                        nostrorum presentium videlicet et futurorum comperiet indu|stria,
                            quod<persName
                            key="#Curtes #Gift #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #vassusOf #fidelisOf #officeHolderFor"
                            ref="#people/3904"> Ruthcherius</persName> quondam <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fidelis</rs>
                        <rs key="#vassusOf">vassus</rs> et <rs key="#officeHolderFor"
                            >ministerialis</rs> noster de hac luce | discedens quandam <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> sue proprietatis nomine <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Gift" ref="#estates/3600"><placeName key="#Curtes #Gift"
                                ref="#places/4920">Ruberino</placeName></geogName> in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/270" key="#Comitatus">comitatu, scilicet | <placeName
                                ref="#places/10" key="#Comitatus">Bergamense</placeName></geogName>,
                        prope <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebem</rs> que dicitur <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3581"><placeName
                                ref="#places/1936" key="#Baptismal_churches">Forum
                            Novum</placeName></orgName>, ad partem <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/224"
                            key="#Gift #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Immunity #Mother_churches"
                            >Ęcclesie <placeName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/58"
                                >Cremo|nensis</placeName></orgName> obtulisset ac<rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"> iure proprietario</rs> pro anime
                        sue remedio per <rs key="#executorOfTheWillOf">rogatores</rs> suos,
                            <persName key="#executorOfTheWillOf"><name ref="Guntherius"
                                >Gunthe|ri</name></persName>, videlicet <persName
                            key="#executorOfTheWillOf"><name ref="Giroldus"
                            >Gyroldum</name></persName> atque <persName key="#executorOfTheWillOf"
                                ><name ref="Hillonis">Hillonem</name></persName>, per <rs
                            key="#Cartula #Offersio/donatio">conscriptionis paginam</rs> tradidit et
                        per fideles | nostros in nostra presentia eandem traditionis paginam quam
                        predictus ille vassus noster | rogatorque ipsius rei fecerat undique
                        roborari iussimus, set pro ampliori firmitate ac to|cius securitatis
                        augmenti placuit nobis id ipsum nostra ac imperiali auctoritate mu|niri. Et
                        ideo anc nostre auctoritatis roborationem superaddentes fieri iussimus, per
                        quam omni|no sancimus firmumque mansurum constituimus, ut nullus comes neque
                        ullus rei pu|blice minister nec quispiam heredum vel proheredum predicti
                        Ruthcheri atque ulla intercidens et | opposita persona quippiam
                        retractationis aut invasionis inquietudinem in his rebus | ullo umquam
                        tempore contra prefatam Ecclesiam aut rectores eius inferre presumat nec
                        quis|quam inde causare conetur, set sicut in nostra presentia tradite et a
                        nostris fidelibus fue|runt roborate, ita nostris et futuris temporibus
                        nostra hac imperiali auctoritate corrobora|te ad partem predicte Cremonensis
                        Ęcclesie iure proprietario maneant inconvulsa | cum omnibus integritatibus,
                        veluti in brevi testato continetur. Si quis autem contra hanc nostram |
                        auctoritatem ire temptaverit ac de prescriptis rebus parte prefate Ęcclesie
                        inquietare que|sierit, penam <rs key="#Immunity">immunitatis</rs> nostre,
                        sicut de rebus ceterarum ęcclesiarum, hoc est triginta | libras argenti ipsi
                        componet Ęcclesie. Et ut hoc certius crederetur ac diligentius |
                        observaretur, de anulo nostro subter iussimus sigillari. <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Plato">P(lat)o</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">not(arius)</rs> ad invicem <persName ref="#people/3906"
                            >Dructemiri </persName>recognovi. Data V idus mar(cii) anno imperii
                        domni Luodovici pii imperatoris in Italia VIII, ind(ictione) VIIII. Actum |
                            <placeName ref="#places/275"
                            key="#Cities #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >Mantua </placeName><rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >palatio regio</rs>, feliciter in Domino amen.</ab>
